question: How many unique authors have written science fiction novels?
query:
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

WHERE {

}

PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

# Recuperar las regiones administrativas que limitan con el Océano Pacífico
SELECT DISTINCT ?region WHERE {
  ?region wdt:P31 wd:Q82794 ;  # wdt:P31 indica que la entidad es una instancia de wd:Q82794 (región administrativa)
          wdt:P461 wd:Q98 .    # wdt:P461 indica que la entidad limita con wd:Q98 (Océano Pacífico)
}

question: List all bands according to the amount of songs they published.
query:
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pv: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/>
PREFIX ecc: <https://ns.eccenca.com/>
PREFIX void: <http://rdfs.org/ns/void#>
PREFIX vann: <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

SELECT ?band (COUNT(?song) AS ?numberOfSongs)
WHERE {
  ?band rdf:type dbo:Band .
  ?song dbo:artist ?band .
}
GROUP BY ?band
ORDER BY DESC(?numberOfSongs)

}

PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>

WHERE {
  ?city rdf:type dbo:City .

  ?country rdf:type dbo:Country .
}

LIMIT 10

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pv: <http://ld.company.org/prod-vocab/>
PREFIX ecc: <https://ns.eccenca.com/>
PREFIX void: <http://rdfs.org/ns/void#>
PREFIX vann: <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Writer> ;
       <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris> .
  ?book <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/author> ?uri .
}
